            "id": 5921843,
            "title": "《北水新貴》阿里成交急增,申洲國際罕有打入十大成交榜",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社3日專訊》據港交所(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00388:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00388\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00388-HK</a>)公布數據,今日「港股通(滬)」及「港股通(深)」十大成交當中,見阿里(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09988:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09988\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09988-HK</a>)、騰訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00700:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00700\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00700-HK</a>)及恒生中國企業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02828:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02828\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02828-HK</a>)涉及北水的成交急增,「港股通(滬)」買入及賣出金額共分別62.87億元、54.72億元及17.08億元;「港股通(深)」買入及賣出金額共分別35.82億元、31.67億元及31.26億元。阿里。騰訊及恒生中國企業全日分別錄得淨買入34.87億元12.15億元及48.33億元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　今日「港股通(滬)」十大成交當中,則見盈富基金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02800:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02800\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02800-HK</a>)及美團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03690:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03690\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03690-HK</a>)涉及北水的成交急增,買入及賣出金額共分別53億元及18.27億元。盈富基金及美團全日分別錄得淨買入52.85億元及7865萬元。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　申洲國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02313-HK</a>)見多日以來首見進佔「港股通(滬)」十大成交之列,「港股通(滬)」北水全日買入5.21億元,賣出5.33億元,淨賣出1164萬元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　北水焦點股</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　=====</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　股份相隔多久再上榜　　　股份名稱　　　　編號　　　　買入及賣出總金額(元)　港股通(滬)　港股通(深)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">-----------------------------------------</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">阿里　　　　　(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09988:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09988\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09988-HK</a>)　　62.87億　(滬)　　　　　上日　　　　　上日</p><tr></tr><tr></tr><tr></tr><tr></tr><tr></tr><tr></tr><tr></tr><tr></tr></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
